accountForBaseToken.t.sol
├── given the ID does not reference a base token position
│  └── it should revert with NotBaseTokenPosition
└── given the ID references a base token position
   ├── given the ID references the accounting token position
   │  ├── it should set position.lastAccountingTime to current block timestmap
   │  ├── it should set position.value to the caliber's accounting token balance
   │  └── it should return the new value and the value change since last accounting
   └─── given the ID references another base token position
      ├── it should set position.lastAccountingTime to current block timestmap
      ├── it should set position.value to the caliber's base token balance converted to accounting token
      └── it should return the new value and the value change since last accounting
